ai-patthana22.14:0.2_0: (These should be expanded as in MN 5.)
ai-patthana22.14:1.1_0: (All should not be explained the teachings.)
ai-patthana22.14:2.1_1: Not reciting the unkilled in the undeclared points, causes and reasons.
ai-patthana22.14:2.1_2: Not declared by an undetermined teaching, the noble ones arises.
ai-patthana22.14:2.1_3: No by nature, nor by nature, nor by declared that this is a cause.
ai-patthana22.14:2.1_4: Nose this is a cause or condition for the unskillful.
